{"tid":1817664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英關注港警理大濫捕醫護","createTime":"2020-01-09T09:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T10:50:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"be541a673a01b375f2cdfe2bf3acadf243f30781","tid":1817664,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:23:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200109/BQG7EJ4KLBQVOWHJ4SXHQ27MKY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200109%2FBQG7EJ4KLBQVOWHJ4SXHQ27MKY%2F&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=4842d101\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200109%2FBQG7EJ4KLBQVOWHJ4SXHQ27MKY%2F&h=0059a291\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200109/BQG7EJ4KLBQVOWHJ4SXHQ27MKY/</a><br />\n<br />\n英關注港警理大濫捕醫護<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200109/large/1578501632_2cd8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200109%2Flarge%2F1578501632_2cd8.jpg&h=aac65c73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLord Ahmad of Wimbledon<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方去年圍攻理工大學，更拘捕大批在場義務醫護人員，事件震動國際。英國外交及聯邦事務部副部長Lord Ahmad of Wimbledon昨回應理大事件，指英國「極度重視對香港醫護人員受不人道對待的指控」，期望香港當局遵守國際人道法律和慣例，因為受傷者能獲得適當醫療救助，以及提供安全通道供希望離開的人都是至關重要的。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：200市民悼梓樂逝世兩月 警拘多人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n籲獨立調查警暴<br />\n<br />\n英國民間組織Hong Kong Watch昨於社交網指，Lord Ahmad回應國會有關反送中人權及警暴問題時，稱英國支持並一直呼籲對最近香港事件進行有力的獨立調查，同時相信英國對當前局勢關注，中國和香港領導均有目共睹。他補充，外交大臣曾於去年11月19日召中國大使表達對香港局勢的關注，英國仍堅守對《中英聯合聲明》所保障的權利和自由的承諾，也將會繼續向香港特區政府和北京當局提出關注。<br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Watch聯合創始人兼主席羅傑斯（Benedict Rogers）表示：「我們歡迎副部長對我們保證英國對這些報道的高度重視。」他們敦促英國政府為此作進一步行動，包括在香港無法就警暴作調查下，進行國際調查，並敦促英政府對嚴重侵犯人權和違反國際人道主義準則的人施加針對性的馬格尼茨基制裁。他敦促首相約翰遜應立即為香港自由、人權和自治發聲，並成立國際聯絡小組以協調全球應對香港危機。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黃頌恩"},{"pid":"dca8f5095161c3e2ae271845b5c6e45c1f60753e","tid":1817664,"uid":98993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:24:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6e5ffb1da689bbd1a02010f8aaf204785502143","tid":1817664,"uid":51057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"一直關注事件"},{"pid":"0617d95da2b91b9e74483051e18b4fdee0a90e8d","tid":1817664,"uid":60563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:24:49.000Z","msg":"多謝晒wor"},{"pid":"be29ad576f72b53d4adceaacd92b26b5de263013","tid":1817664,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:25:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kZaFTRi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkZaFTRi.gif&h=62a9d79a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be0d307c6037de32fe667698431946c0d5b4c5ba","tid":1817664,"uid":191812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:25:24.000Z","msg":"一直關注，直到永遠，阿門"},{"pid":"05c36ef03939629bd1f0460f2b56bee2725bfb4f","tid":1817664,"uid":230662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:25:26.000Z","msg":"關注國"},{"pid":"d40631b6bb77303584248bf51af59acdf3314909","tid":1817664,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:25:31.000Z","msg":"迖狗上身"},{"pid":"de0224432d26de6aae73b4b07db463d875a7505e","tid":1817664,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"英國簡體達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ec424fee34ea8f2fa012a611918a10f92401c2","tid":1817664,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f0512b7cc2391cfc0f2e43cd185b3715d5ba10fe","tid":1817664,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score